race.comment: HOLY RACKET (9) has a solid record over this sprint trip with four wins and four placings from 12 attempts and is drawn to sit up on speed from the low draw. Has placed two from two over this course and distance and looks the one they all have to run down. CIFRADO (1) will strip fitter third-up from the spell and has a bit of class over this field. A better showing would not surprise. HURTS SO GOOD (6) will be rock-hard fit and gets Thompson on board for the Gollan stable. Do not dismiss lighty. MANHOOD (2) grows a leg for hoop Guthmann-Chester who has only missed a place once in eight career rides. In the mix.
